          <li><strong>Point agents</strong> — one job, one workflow. Apollo (data), Clay (enrichment), Coldreach (signals).</li>
          <li><strong>Full-stack agents</strong> — research, write, send, follow up across email + LinkedIn. Artisan, 11x.ai, AiSDR.</li>
          <li><strong>Engagement platforms with AI</strong> — established sales platforms with AI bolted on. Outreach, Salesloft, Amplemarket.</li>
        </ol>

        <p>The right pick depends on what your existing team already does. Replacing nothing is harder than augmenting one role.</p>

